---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../utils/constants';

const lang = 'ms';
const post = {
  title: 'Bank Tolak Prime Mover 2026 - Alternatif 0% Deposit',
  slug: 'prime-mover-bank-tolak-2026',
  excerpt: 'Bank tolak pembiayaan prime mover? Jangan putus asa. Ing Heng tawarkan alternatif 0% deposit, 100% pinjaman, tiada had umur. Dapatkan kelulusan 24-48 jam walaupun bank tolak.',
  date: '2026-01-08',
  author: 'Pasukan Ing Heng Credit',
  readTime: 5,
  category: 'Pembiayaan Jentera',
  image: '/images/blog/bank-rejected.jpg'
};

const keywords = ['pembiayaan jentera', 'bank tolak', 'prime mover', 'alternatif'];
const breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Utama', href: '/ms' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/ms/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/ms/blog/${post.slug}` }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BlogPosting",
      "headline": post.title,
      "description": post.excerpt,
      "datePublished": post.date,
      "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": post.author },
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "Ing Heng Credit & Leasing Sdn Bhd",
        "logo": {
          "@type": "ImageObject",
          "url": "https://inghengcredit.com/logo.png"
        }
      }
    }
  </script>

  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Pembiayaan Jentera</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
        <span>{post.author}</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('ms-MY', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>{post.readTime} min bacaan</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>Bank Tolak? Jangan Putus Asa</h2>

      <p>Bank sering menolak pembiayaan prime mover untuk pelbagai sebab: kredit buruk, syarikat baru, pendapatan tidak mencukupi, atau alasan lain.</p>

      <p>Tetapi ini bukan bermakna anda tidak boleh dapatkan pembiayaan. Ing Heng menawarkan alternatif yang lebih fleksibel.</p>

      <h2>Mengapa Bank Tolak?</h2>

      <p>Bank menolak pembiayaan prime mover kerana:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Kredit buruk:</strong> Masalah CCRIS/CTOS</li>
        <li><strong>Syarikat baru:</strong> Kurang dari 2 tahun</li>
        <li><strong>Pendapatan rendah:</strong> Tidak memenuhi ratio</li>
        <li><strong>Umur prime mover:</strong> Melebihi 5 tahun</li>
        <li><strong>Deposit tidak mencukupi:</strong> Tak ada 10-20% down payment</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Penyelesaian Ing Heng: Alternatif Fleksibel</h2>

      <p>Ing Heng Credit menawarkan pembiayaan prime mover yang lebih fleksibel:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Kredit buruk OK</strong> - berasaskan pendapatan</li>
        <li><strong>Syarikat baru OK</strong> - fokus pada potensi</li>
        <li><strong>Umur tiada had</strong> - biayai sehingga 10 tahun</li>
        <li><strong>0% deposit</strong> - tiada bayaran muka</li>
        <li><strong>Kelulusan pantas</strong> - 24-48 jam</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Hubungi Kami Hari Ini</h2>

      <p>Bank tolak? Dapatkan pembiayaan prime mover 0% deposit dengan Ing Heng.</p>

      <div style="background: #F5F0E8; border-left: 4px solid #D4A574; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <h3 style="color: #2D1810; margin-top: 0;">Bank Tolak?</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Dapatkan kelulusan pembiayaan 0% deposit walaupun bank tolak dalam 24-48 jam. WhatsApp kami untuk konsultasi percuma.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Hubungi:</strong> +60175700889 (WhatsApp) | 03-3324 8899 (Telefon)</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t">
      <CTAButton text="Dapatkan Alternatif" link={COMPANY_INFO.whatsapp.link} variant="accent" size="large" />
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h2 {
    color: #2D1810;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #D4A574;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  h3 {
    color: #8B6F47;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  strong {
    color: #2D1810;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  li {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #D4A574;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
